HY-5Aj","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":1795,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/30\/lord-father-adam-one\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":0},"title":"Farewell Sermon: Your Lord is one, your father is one","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Nadrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said during the days after the pilgrimage, \u201cO people, your Lord is one and your father Adam is one. There is no favor of an Arab over a foreigner, nor a foreigner over an Arab, and neither\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21900,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/12\/sent-prophet-perfect-good-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Morals: Allah sent the Prophet to perfect good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 12, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has sent me with the perfection of noble morals and completion of good deeds.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Awsat\u0323 7073 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/best-long-lives-good-deeds\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Life: Best Muslims have long lives full of good deeds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Busr reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, who are the best people?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOne with a long life of good deeds.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2329 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u064f\u0633\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064b\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15083,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/16\/prophet-sawm-monday-thursday\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siyam: The Prophet loved to fast Monday, Thursday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe deeds are presented on Monday and Thursday. Thus, I love for\u00a0my deeds to be\u00a0presented while I am fasting.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 747 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41150,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/08\/zubayr-secret\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":4},"title":"Zubayr on Sincerity: Keep some of your good deeds private","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 8, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qays reported: Al-Zubayr ibn al-\u2018Awwam, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever among you can keep some of his good deeds hidden, let him do so.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 34751 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0632\u0650\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0632\u064f\u0651\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0648\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19246,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/05\/28\/long-life-many-hasanat\/","url_meta":{"origin":21471,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Life: Best people have long lives, many good deeds","autho